{"id": "1285582447098073198", "channel_id": "1283058480323891331", "type": 0, "author_id": "1231540652253253705", "author_name": "menoctus", "author_bot": false, "content": "中篇地圖", "timestamp": "2024-09-17T12:45:40.355000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1285582446401687633", "filename": "8.2low.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2042075, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1283058480323891331/1285582446401687633/8.2low.jpg?ex=69cbc1f4&is=69ca7074&hm=bf2816933f7c91abc39f024fd1671dda3b21cbb81841a37884a3048b9b43e978&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1283058480323891331", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "第8章「終末交響曲」關卡地圖總覽", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1283686881858420777", "1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1285582904272883753", "channel_id": "1285582904272883753", "type": 0, "author_id": "1231540652253253705", "author_name": "menoctus", "author_bot": false, "content": "> 大家好，這裡是難忘今宵攻略組，本期為大家帶來的是第17期「融災禁區」地圖。\n\n◆每兩週刷新獎勵與關卡，每個關卡只需要完成普通模式、困難或癲狂模式其中之一。\n\n◆經過毒地板（紫色格子）時，會扣除 血量上限 的約5%，也就是固定值。\n\n當踏入毒地板所扣除的血量被判定為致命傷害，則觸發死亡抵抗/復活確認。\n\n◆同一關卡的各級警示地圖都相同。\n\n▼▼▼\n\n【第1波】特遣紀錄 - 莉莉「故事的魔法」-【安迪·約翰遜之力】地圖\n【第2波】無光之境 - 間隙 地圖【混沌8，深海6，血肉4，超維2】\n【第3波】落地戰\n【第4波】特遣紀錄 - 索蕾爾「薔薇禮贊」-【墜落的審判】地圖\n【第5波】如圖\n\nuid: 100001547", "timestamp": "2024-09-17T12:47:29.354000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1285582907079000144", "filename": "17low.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 14793471, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1285582904272883753/1285582907079000144/17low.jpg?ex=69cbc262&is=69ca70e2&hm=f7887674ffa5b1067968c459f1500442558e5a44147c9778775e54c9405e89dd&"}, {"id": "1285582908014198844", "filename": "3.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 361386, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1285582904272883753/1285582908014198844/3.jpg?ex=69cbc262&is=69ca70e2&hm=65c4c89acd9dc20c3ff102e965dfd04f9d5b7913501062b64a4ba21b158d483c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1285582904272883753", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關卡地圖「融災禁區」總覽ⅩⅦ", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1283686881858420777", "1181143392739147778"]}
